{% extends "./layouts/base.html" %}

{% block body %}

  {% dnd_area 'dnd_area'
    label='Home template',
    class='home-template'
  %}

  {# The goto tool for Power BI Tabular modelling #}
  {% include_dnd_partial path='../sections/text-big-image.html' context={} %}

  {# Streamline, automate & boost perfomance with the ultimate Power BI modelling tool #}
  {% include_dnd_partial path='../sections/three-column-icon-text-button.html' context={} %}

  {# Time to use your time better #}
  {% include_dnd_partial path='../sections/text-video.html' context={} %}

  {# Time to use your time better #}
  {% include_dnd_partial path='../sections/image-text-list.html' context={} %}

  {# Trusted by 50 000 + customers #}
  {% dnd_section
    padding={
      "default" : {
        "bottom" : "30px"
      }
    }
  %}
    {% dnd_column
      offset=0,
      width=12
    %}
      {% dnd_row %}
        {% dnd_module
          path="/tabulareditor-nimbly-lite-child-2024/modules/unicard",
          offset=0,
          width=12,
          module_components=[ "main_heading" ],
          heading={
            "heading_style" : "display-4",
            "heading_text" : "Trusted by 50 000 + customers",
            "heading_text_prop_visibility" : true
          }
        %}
        {% end_dnd_module %}
      {% end_dnd_row %}
    {% end_dnd_column %}
  {% end_dnd_section %}

  {# Carousel autoscroll #}
  {% include_dnd_partial path='../sections/carousel-autoscroll.html' context={} %}

  {# What are people saying about TE3? #}
  {% dnd_section
    padding={
      "default" : {
        "bottom" : "20px"
      }
    }
  %}
    {% dnd_column
      offset=0,
      width=6
    %}
      {% dnd_row %}
        {% dnd_module
          path="/tabulareditor-nimbly-lite-child-2024/modules/unicard",
          offset=0,
          width=12,
          heading={
            "heading_style" : "display-4",
            "heading_text" : "What are people saying about TE3?",
            "heading_text_prop_visibility" : true
          },
          module_components=[ "main_heading" ]
        %}
        {% end_dnd_module %}
      {% end_dnd_row %}
    {% end_dnd_column %}
    {% dnd_column
      offset=6,
      width=6
    %}

    {% end_dnd_column %}
  {% end_dnd_section %}

  {# Quote carousel #}
  {% include_dnd_partial path='../sections/quote-carousel.html' context={} %}

  {# Let us show you how TE3 can elevate your data modeling! #}
  {% include_dnd_partial path='../sections/big-image-box-text.html' context={} %}

  {% end_dnd_area %}

{% endblock body %}
